```csharp
public void GetTwoValues(ref int a, ref string b)
{
    a = 123;
    b = "Hello World!";
}

// 调用示例
int a = 0;
string b = "";
GetTwoValues(ref a, ref b);
Console.WriteLine($"a={a}, b={b}");
```

